messageBody:
There must be a problem with your download of the file as it displays perfectly for me.

I am emailing the file direct to you Paul.

Moira

On 16/11/2007, Paul Tremblay <phthenry@...> wrote:

Read_Alphabet@yahoogroups.com wrote:
>
>
>
> Hello,
>
> This email message is a notification to let you know that
> a file has been uploaded to the Files area of the Read_Alphabet
> group.
>

This PDF appears as mostly a series of boxes for me. How did you
translate it to PDF? Could Moiria repost the original so I could try to
convert it to PDF as well?

Paul




--
